      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRESIDENT ROLEX (1) pinged the lids and led for most of the way to hold a minor placing when second and beaten 1.5 lengths (30.01) at Wentworth Park in a Grade 5 over 520m. Deserves serious consideration. EL REY (2) jumped from this box and placed but in quick time latest (34.77) at this track over 600m in a Grade 5. Bold showing expected again. ZIPPING PFEIFFER (6) is progressing well scoring last time out (29.76) at this track and bringing up her 8th career win. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Capable of going well again. JASPER DARKE (4) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
